Additionally, remove the ManageEpisode() method from the FoodSpawner script and handle it in the "PlayerAgent" script so that each agent can manage their episodes independently.

Lastly, increase the batch_size and buffer_size in your circletest.yaml configuration file. The small values might be causing some agents to only learn to move in an upper-right direction. Try batch_size: 128 and buffer_size: 1024.

